1
00:00:05,020 --> 00:00:07,500
♪That dangerous temptation♪

2
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:10,020
♪Like a whirlpool churning deep♪

3
00:00:10,060 --> 00:00:12,900
♪Like a moth darts into the flame♪

4
00:00:12,940 --> 00:00:14,340
♪Falling towards the light♪

5
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:17,420
♪Watch as everything drowns in shadows♪

6
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:19,340
♪Have no fear, do not retreat♪

7
00:00:19,940 --> 00:00:23,220
♪See the blazing sparks ignite♪

8
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:27,060
♪Believe this all has cause and effect♪

9
00:00:27,100 --> 00:00:29,460
♪No evil escapes untouched♪

10
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:31,820
♪From the stormy torrents in this life♪

11
00:00:32,060 --> 00:00:34,850
♪The memories howl as they flash by♪

12
00:00:34,850 --> 00:00:37,820
[Miss Mystery]

13
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:41,000
This is the suitcase of Lin Bao'er
with a combination lock.

14
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:42,600
It must contain her secrets.

15
00:00:45,440 --> 00:00:46,160
Open it.

16
00:01:13,980 --> 00:01:16,380
[Lianhe Police Station's Secrets]

17
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:22,100
[Store Safeguarding, 49 yuan]

18
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:30,520
What's all this?

19
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:33,360
Check it out yourself!

20
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:49,000
Darn!

21
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,200
Darn!

22
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:55,600
Yang Jian,

23
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,160
how dare you embezzle so much money
behind my back!

24
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,160
Bao'er, here's a wedding gift for you.

25
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:07,080
The evidence of Yang Jian's
dirty laundry in my dad's business.

26
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:21,220
[Episode 7]

27
00:02:26,480 --> 00:02:27,280
Take care.

28
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,320
Don't worry.

29
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:32,360
Since I'm here with you,
what's there to worry about?

30
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:34,840
Promise me,

31
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,400
don't act alone again.

32
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,280
Okay.

33
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,800
Thank you for your wedding gift.

34
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,680
If you keep risking your life like this,

35
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,600
it won't be worth the gift.

36
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:50,800
Get some rest.

37
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:55,040
Thank you for saving me.

38
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,320
What did you just say?

39
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,040
I said,

40
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:06,280
thank you for saving me.

41
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,480
Well,

42
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:11,960
I'm your husband.

43
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,760
It's my pleasure to do that.

44
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,480
Bear the pain for a while.

45
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,160
Mr. Zhu,

46
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:32,040
we're just partners.

47
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:39,600
How can you be so devoted?

48
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,040
Are you so innocent?

49
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:48,880
Lin Bao'er,

50
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:52,200
I've never cared so deeply
about someone before.

51
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,640
I don't need your care.

52
00:03:59,080 --> 00:03:59,720
Okay.

53
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,640
You don't need me.

54
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:09,120
And you've never told me the truth.

55
00:04:16,840 --> 00:04:17,480
All right.

56
00:04:19,400 --> 00:04:21,720
Tell me what happened to your shoulder.

57
00:04:22,080 --> 00:04:23,280
You don't need to know that.

58
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,440
You show up in Lianhe Town,

59
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:28,000
approach me,

60
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,200
and use me.

61
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,480
Don't I...

62
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,040
Don't I have the right to know anything?

63
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,840
Since you know I'm using you,

64
00:04:36,760 --> 00:04:38,520
then just play along with the show.

65
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,760
Why do you take it so seriously?

66
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,800
300 taels, 500 taels.

67
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,720
How dare you embezzle so much
behind my back?

68
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:11,360
Mayor.

69
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:11,960
Oh no,

70
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,920
Master Dou, pretty please.

71
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,160
For all these years,

72
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,760
I have been your devoted follower;

73
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:18,240
please save me this time.

74
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,240
I beg your forgiveness!

75
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,600
Since your hands are so dirty,

76
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,600
what's the point

77
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,520
in keeping them?

78
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:38,280
Master, pretty please!

79
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,640
I swear, I promise,

80
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,040
I won't dare to commit it again.

81
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:41,680
I beg you.

82
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,680
I was wrong...

83
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:45,440
Please save me this time.

84
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:47,760
Save you?

85
00:05:48,320 --> 00:05:50,600
Your dirty laundry involves Master Zhu!

86
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,040
Even if I want to save you,

87
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,240
will Master Zhu agree?

88
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,400
Want to prove your determination?

89
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,920
Then don't just talk.

90
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,120
Enough!

91
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,320
For all these years,

92
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:36,040
you have been my devoted follower.

93
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,440
I'll save you one last time.

94
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,160
Thank you,

95
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,400
thank you, master.

96
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,280
I was really wrong.

97
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,400
I have been tempted.

98
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,400
I shouldn't have been that greedy.

99
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,160
But with Lin Bao'er,

100
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,560
we should never underestimate her.

101
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:56,520
If she can outsmart us
in front of Master Zhu this time,

102
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:57,880
I am sure that she'll do something

103
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:01,720
even worse for us in the future.

104
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,040
You have three days.

105
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:14,200
You have three days to deal with her.

106
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,640
Otherwise,

107
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:23,080
don't blame me for being ruthless.

108
00:07:37,460 --> 00:07:39,980
[Huamei Clothing Store]

109
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:41,280
Rickshaw!

110
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,280
Madam,

111
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,800
see you tomorrow in my store.

112
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:53,800
At 3:00 p.m., please don't forget it.

113
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:05,880
One more chance.

114
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:07,240
Where is it?

115
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,640
Dream on! You'll never know!

116
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:20,760
(After all these years,
I still can't find it.)

117
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:28,880
(It must still be in this manor.)

118
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:32,520
(Xue Tao, you're really something.)

119
00:08:41,660 --> 00:08:43,000
Come see my merchandise!

120
00:08:47,710 --> 00:08:49,790
Lanterns!

121
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,800
Rickshaw!

122
00:09:12,540 --> 00:09:15,060
♪The end has now been reached♪

123
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:17,980
♪Yet we face each other in silence♪

124
00:09:18,700 --> 00:09:21,340
♪Looking away from you♪

125
00:09:21,340 --> 00:09:25,300
♪Emotions like a flood
they spread and grew♪

126
00:09:25,580 --> 00:09:28,820
♪Who would like to be fooled♪

127
00:09:29,900 --> 00:09:33,940
♪Love, how could it be a lie♪

128
00:09:37,500 --> 00:09:40,500
♪In a moment♪

129
00:09:40,540 --> 00:09:43,420
♪Flitting images flashing♪

130
00:09:43,700 --> 00:09:45,780
♪Eyes fall shut♪

131
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:49,460
♪Fingertips gently touched♪

132
00:09:50,420 --> 00:09:52,980
♪Risking fate and danger venturing♪

133
00:09:53,020 --> 00:09:54,900
♪Dancing on the tip of the knife♪

134
00:09:55,020 --> 00:10:01,180
♪Put on a show wholeheartedly♪

135
00:10:02,100 --> 00:10:05,340
♪In a moment♪

136
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:08,260
♪The memory in my mind♪

137
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:10,380
♪Surging at me♪

138
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:14,540
♪Beliefs hidden deep inside♪

139
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:17,660
♪In an abyss perhaps inescapable♪

140
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:20,820
♪Under a ray of light in the darkness♪

141
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:22,820
♪I may reopen my eyes♪
